import React from 'react'


const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <FooterContainer>
            <FooterWrap>
                <SocialMedia>
                    <SocialMediaWrap>
                        <SocialLogo to="/">Subliminals</SocialLogo>
                        <SocialIcons>
                            <SocialIconLink href='/' target="_blank"
                            arial-label="Instagram" rel='noopener noreferer'>
                                <FaInstagram />
                            </SocialIconLink>
                            <SocialIconLink href='/' target="_blank"
                            arial-label="Gmail" rel='noopener noreferer'>
                                <FaMail/>
                            </SocialIconLink>
                        </SocialIcons>
                    </SocialMediaWrap>
                </SocialMedia>
            </FooterWrap>
        </FooterContainer>
    )
}

export default Footer
